## Session 4: Advanced CSS

Advanced CSS features enable expressive, maintainable, and performant user interfaces without JavaScript.

### CSS Custom Properties (Variables)

```css
/* Define on :root for global access */
:root {
  /* Design tokens */
  --color-primary-400: #818cf8;
  --color-primary-600: #4f46e5;
  --color-primary-800: #3730a3;

  --font-size-sm: 0.875rem;
  --font-size-base: 1rem;
  --font-size-lg: 1.125rem;

  --spacing-1: 0.25rem;
  --spacing-2: 0.5rem;
  --spacing-4: 1rem;
  --spacing-8: 2rem;

  --border-radius: 0.5rem;
  --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
  --transition-base: 150ms ease;
}

/* Dark mode via custom property overrides */
@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  :root {
    --color-bg: #0f172a;
    --color-text: #e2e8f0;
    --color-surface: #1e293b;
  }
}

[data-theme="dark"] {
  --color-bg: #0f172a;
  --color-text: #e2e8f0;
}

/* Local scope override */
.card {
  --card-padding: var(--spacing-4);
  padding: var(--card-padding);
}
.card.compact {
  --card-padding: var(--spacing-2); /* only affects this card */
}
```

### Transitions

```css
/* transition: property duration timing-function delay */
.button {
  background: var(--color-primary-600);
  transform: translateY(0);
  box-shadow: none;
  /* Only transition specific properties — avoid 'transition: all' */
  transition:
    background-color var(--transition-base),
    transform 150ms ease,
    box-shadow 150ms ease;
}

.button:hover {
  background: var(--color-primary-800);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
}

/* Accessible: respect user preference */
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *, *::before, *::after {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}
```

### Keyframe Animations

```css
/* Define the animation */
@keyframes fadeInUp {
  from {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
  }
  to {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
}

@keyframes spin {
  to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}

@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
  50%       { opacity: 0.5; }
}

/* Apply */
.card {
  animation: fadeInUp 0.4s ease both;
  /* name duration timing fill-mode */
}

.loading-spinner {
  animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
}

.skeleton {
  animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  background: #e2e8f0;
}

/* Staggered children */
.stagger-children > * {
  animation: fadeInUp 0.3s ease both;
}
.stagger-children > *:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0ms; }
.stagger-children > *:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 100ms; }
.stagger-children > *:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 200ms; }
```

### Pseudo-elements and Pseudo-classes

```css
/* ::before and ::after — decorative content */
.badge::before {
  content: '';
  display: inline-block;
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: currentColor;
  margin-right: 0.5rem;
}

.section-title::after {
  content: '';
  display: block;
  width: 3rem;
  height: 3px;
  background: var(--color-primary-600);
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
}

/* Useful pseudo-classes */
:is(h1, h2, h3) { line-height: 1.2; }  /* :is() matches any */
:where(p, li)   { max-width: 65ch; }    /* :where() — zero specificity */

.input:focus-visible { outline: 3px solid var(--color-primary-400); }
/* :focus-visible shows outline for keyboard, not mouse click */

.list-item:not(:last-child) { border-bottom: 1px solid; }

/* :has() — parent selector */
.card:has(img) { grid-template-rows: auto 1fr; }
.form:has(:invalid) .submit-btn { opacity: 0.5; }
```

